text: Mary Ann R Tadd (born 1936), is a female former athlete who competed for England. ==Athletics career== She represented England in the javelin at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games in Cardiff, Wales. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:English female javelin throwers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games Category:Living people
title: Mary Tadd
